== Configurar SSH

Ainda como root

nano /etc/ssh/sshd_config

Porta 65522
LoginGraceTime 30
PermitRootLogin no
PasswordAuthentication no
MaxAuthTries 3
X11Forwarding no
DenyUsers root
AllowUsers ribafs

sudo service ssh restart

== Sincronizar a chave do ssh do desktop para o servidor

apt install rsync

rsync --archive --chown=ribafs:ribafs ~/.ssh /home/ribafs

Testar

Conectar com ribafs

exit

ssh -p 65522 ribafs@45.56.107.114

cd ~/


ReferÃªncias
https://kifarunix.com/allow-deny-specific-users-to-login-via-ssh-on-ubuntu-18-04/

reboot


